    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "evidence_text",
      "x": 96,
      "y": 772,
      "width": 1320,
      "height": 142,
      "text": "Evidence / hot-path commands\n\nmemd memory --quality --summary --root .memd\nMEMD_TAB_ID=tab-alpha memd status --summary --output .memd\nmemd resume --output .memd --intent current_task\n\nThe same compiled pages are the truth surface; semantic recall points back to them.",
      "originalText": "Evidence / hot-path commands\n\nmemd memory --quality --summary --root .memd\nMEMD_TAB_ID=tab-alpha memd status --summary --output .memd\nmemd resume --output .memd --intent current_task\n\nThe same compiled pages are the truth surface; semantic recall points back to them.",
